# Build context for the rat daemon image (core/Dockerfile → core + contracts) AND the
# plugin images (plugins/<plugin>/Dockerfile, platform/bff → plugins/platform + the
# python SDK). Allow those trees; aggressively exclude the heavy junk (plugins/ alone is
# ~59M of node_modules/__pycache__ otherwise).
# (`!examples` became `!plugins` with the ADR-038 move — the stale allowlist had silently
# broken every plugin-image build; found while packaging vault-py, DX-6.)
*
!core
!contracts
!plugins
!platform
plugins/**/node_modules
plugins/**/__pycache__
plugins/**/*.vsix
platform/**/__pycache__
**/target
**/logs
**/.git
